text.section:
To be eligible for a grant under § 7-1003 of this subtitle, a Program applicant shall:
Provide door-to-door transportation for low-income to moderate-income seniors who have difficulty accessing or using other existing transportation systems;
Use primarily volunteer drivers who drive their own vehicles;
Use a dispatcher system to respond quickly to requests from low-income to moderate-income seniors for door-to-door transportation; and
Define a geographic area for which door-to-door transportation is provided.
